gov.nih.nlm.meme.common
Interface SemanticType

All Known Implementing Classes:
ConceptSemanticType, SemanticType.Default
public interface SemanticType

Generically represents a semantic type. This class rouhgly corresponds to things like SRDEF and the MID semantic_types table.

Author:
MEME Group
